OL,7,FThey also said that while Israel
OL,8,Fprovided repeated assurances about
OL,9,Facting legally, some of the
OL,10,F"troubling" rhetoric from Benjamin
OL,11,FNetanyahu's government did cast doubt
OL,12,Fon the interpretation and
OL,13,Fimplementation of IHL.
