OL,7,FForeign Secretary David Cameron
OL,8,Freceived the advice on December 8 and
OL,9,Fwas asked to choose to make a
OL,10,Frecommendation from three options: not
OL,11,Fsuspending or revoking arms licenses
OL,12,Fbut keeping them under careful review;
OL,13,Fsuspending any licenses that might be
OL,14,Fused by the IDF in this conflict; or
